subjective.chief_complaint: Dry itchy skin on chest and back, sore and cracked

Patient tried over-the-counter steroid cream last night with minimal effect. Patient also tried antihistamines.

findings: No shortness of breath or cough
physical_exam.text_raw: systemically well no fevers no vomit no SOB/cough no bowel sx
